2012;;California Solo;;American;;Marshall Lewy;;Robert Carlyle, Kathleen Wilhoite, Michael Des Barres, Danny Masterson;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/California_Solo;;Robert Carlyle plays Lachlan MacAldonich, a former Britpop rocker-turned-agricultural worker, who gets caught driving drunk and faces deportation after living in Los Angeles for 12 years. His efforts to stay in the U.S. force him to confront his past and current demons. The film addresses immigration issues, alcoholism, and personal redemption.